    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/548370/extras/8a475ca8e9b2acf4be8dc70c271c7793.poster.avif?t=1631541797\" width=616 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/548370/extras/8a475ca8e9b2acf4be8dc70c271c7793.webm?t=1631541797\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/548370/extras/8a475ca8e9b2acf4be8dc70c271c7793.mp4?t=1631541797\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Rezrog 的土地正动荡不安。来自远方的邪恶巫师和可怕怪物已经降临地球最黑暗的深渊，并在那里攫取强效宝石的能量。你必须带领麾下的一队英雄打败阻拦在你面前的所有人，力争让 Rezrog 恢复昔日和平安乐的景象。<br><br>一路不断装备、制造并升级物品，构建起强大而坚韧的团队，使团队即使面临最庞大且最卑鄙的敌人，也能够承受最猛烈的攻击。在危机四伏的旅程中，通过 100 个地牢关卡学习强大的技能，这将使你在战斗中具有优势，因为你会注意运用战术计谋打败阻挡你前行的一切敌人或障碍。找对方法，就可以向目标再迈进一步。一步走错，就会沦为阶下囚…或面临更糟糕的下场。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/548370/extras/b28435ecca72327ee93af916fe67a433.avif?t=1631541797\" width=615 height=80 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特点</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/548370/extras/3dfd048ceaeb113edbef94228b1c6f13.webp?t=1631541797\" width=15 height=15 /></span>   <strong>独特的团队运作方式</strong> 你麾下有一队勇敢的英雄任你差遣，每位英雄都具有独特的外貌和强项，但每次只有其中的一位英雄可以参与冒险。如果一位英雄被敌军俘获，请用另一位成员将其救出！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/548370/extras/f2ae12f6cb6417098fb2249215f8ef76.webp?t=1631541797\" width=12 height=12 /></span>   <strong>战术回合制对决:</strong> 仔细规划你在战斗中的行动，节省资源，并利用敌人的弱点。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/548370/extras/389d1e6e74b8047ee6c900784c6ba150.webp?t=1631541797\" width=15 height=15 /></span>  <strong>地牢各不相同:</strong> 程序生成的地牢凭借趣味横生的地牢场景、各式各样的装备物品和影响地牢探险的活动，将为每位玩家打造独一无二的体验。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/548370/extras/c94c778b15a5d2a4f34782fb25da5e6a.webp?t=1631541797\" width=15 height=15 /></span>   <strong>永久死亡:</strong> 全员被俘意味着你这支无畏的英雄队伍将迎来旅程的终结。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/548370/extras/f85b4648d46efa53d93ec1759da94bcb.webp?t=1631541797\" width=15 height=15 /></span>   <strong>进度存留:</strong> 你可以通过获取和锻造贵重的宝石将遗产留给下一代英雄（即使在永久死亡后），这样做可以留下点数用于新游戏。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/548370/extras/a21ca78f7ba6b8eff32ccdebc08b849d.webp?t=1631541797\" width=15 height=15 /></span>  <strong>桌游审美:</strong> 模仿纸质桌面游戏风格。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/548370/extras/1dbc1fcb3a31d6b63f8051e9dd173110.webp?t=1631541797\" width=15 height=15 /></span>  <strong>冒险者成长为英雄:</strong> 在团队中分享并配备所有的装备和技能，以适应你的游戏风格，但请平均地配备装备和技能。如果你麾下实力最强的英雄被俘，你将面临一项艰巨的任务。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/548370/extras/3dfd048ceaeb113edbef94228b1c6f13.webp?t=1631541797\" width=15 height=15 /></span>   <strong>地牢探险:</strong> 在面临各种地牢挑战时，为应对不可预见的事件做好准备，注意避开陷阱和致命的遭遇。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/548370/extras/f2ae12f6cb6417098fb2249215f8ef76.webp?t=1631541797\" width=12 height=12 /></span>   <strong>技能系统:</strong> 技能发现和升级系统将允许你在玩游戏的过程中获取和提高技能。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/548370/extras/389d1e6e74b8047ee6c900784c6ba150.webp?t=1631541797\" width=15 height=15 /></span>   <strong>终极怪物之战:</strong> 充满挑战性的终极怪物之战将测试你的战斗意志。一步走错就可能满盘皆输。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/548370/extras/c94c778b15a5d2a4f34782fb25da5e6a.webp?t=1631541797\" width=15 height=15 /></span>  <strong>可供探索的广阔世界:</strong> 100 个地牢关卡，10 个不同的环境。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/548370/extras/f85b4648d46efa53d93ec1759da94bcb.webp?t=1631541797\" width=15 height=15 /></span>   可体验 7 个人物类别。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/548370/extras/a21ca78f7ba6b8eff32ccdebc08b849d.webp?t=1631541797\" width=15 height=15 /></span>   可升级 60 多种技能以提升实力。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/548370/extras/1dbc1fcb3a31d6b63f8051e9dd173110.webp?t=1631541797\" width=15 height=15 /></span>   将遭遇 120 多个敌人。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/548370/extras/1d7dfdbe73fb88b257dfbd6f2b84d55b.avif?t=1631541797\" width=615 height=154 /></span>",
